{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make the registration to the Prompt Payment Code mandatory for all companies",
        "additional_details": "We think mandatory registration:\r\n1. Ensure Fairness: Create a level playing field for businesses of all sizes.\r\n2. Protect SMEs: Prevent smaller companies from suffering due to delayed payments.\r\n3. Boost Economic Stability: Timely payments improve cash flow, enabling businesses to invest, grow, and retain employees.\r\n4. Promote Ethical Business Practices: Encourage companies to prioritise financial responsibility and transparency.",
        "background": "Legislate Mandatory Registration to the Prompt Payment Code and introduce Penalties for failure to comply.",
